TEXT.TITLE: WINCHELL'S DONUT <WDH> SETS INITIAL QUARTERLY
TEXT.BODY: Winchell's Donut Houses LP said it has declared an initial quarterly dividend of 45 cts per unit on Class A and Class B limited partnership units, payable May 29 to holders of record March 31. Reuter
